<refentry id="samba-bgqd.8">

<refmeta>
	<refentrytitle>samba-bgqd</refentrytitle>
	<manvolnum>8</manvolnum>
	<refmiscinfo class="source">Samba</refmiscinfo>
	<refmiscinfo class="manual">System Administration tools</refmiscinfo>
	<refmiscinfo class="version">4.23.4</refmiscinfo>
</refmeta>


<refnamediv>
	<refname>samba-bgqd</refname>
	<refpurpose>This is an internal helper program performing
	asynchronous printing-related tasks</refpurpose>
</refnamediv>

<refsynopsisdiv>
	<cmdsynopsis sepchar=" ">
		<literal>samba-bgqd</literal>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">-D|--daemon</arg>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">-i|--interactive</arg>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">-F|--foreground</arg>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">--no-process-group</arg>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">-d &lt;debug level&gt;</arg>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">--debug-stdout</arg>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">--configfile=&lt;configuration file&gt;</arg>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">--option=&lt;name&gt;=&lt;value&gt;</arg>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">-l|--log-basename &lt;log directory&gt;</arg>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">--ready-signal-fd &lt;fd&gt;</arg>
		<arg choice="opt" rep="norepeat">--parent-watch-fd &lt;fd&gt;</arg>
	</cmdsynopsis>
</refsynopsisdiv>

<refsect1>
	<title>DESCRIPTION</title>

	<para>This program is part of the
	<citerefentry><refentrytitle>samba</refentrytitle>
	<manvolnum>7</manvolnum></citerefentry> suite.</para>

	<para><literal>samba-bgqd</literal> is not intended to be invoked
	directly by users.</para>

	<para>Likewise, while <literal>samba-bgqd</literal> is also not
	intended to be run manually by system administrators, on systems with a
	large number of printers configured via CUPS, it is recommended to run
	<literal>samba-bgqd</literal> as a systemd service to improve
	performance and responsiveness of printing operations.</para>
</refsect1>

